TEXAS REAL ESTATE EXECUTIVES, THE DANIELS GROUP - GILMER

data.description: Looking for a peaceful home in the country with income potential? Come see this charming brick home with three bedrooms and two full baths, located on 46+ acres close to Gilmer for all of your shopping needs! Easy access to Longview, Tyler and a quick two hours to Dallas. There are numerous out buildings including a 1,000 square foot barn, a 588 square foot workshop with electricity, two carports, and a couple of storage buildings. The property consists of a 5-acre homesite with areas set up for livestock & chickens, an 8 acre tract of recently fertilized costal hay and a 33 acre hard wood tree farm for timber, hunting and recreational use. The large pond at the base of the pasture is stocked with Bass, Perch & Crappie and is ready for your fishing pole. This property is currently set up with an agricultural exemption which helps reduce the annual property taxes, currently 655.00. Call today for your private showing!
